summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx addressed to Jeffrey E. Epstein for shipping services rendered. It details the charges incurred, including duties and taxes, and provides a summary of the payment due. The invoice highlights the shipping details and the total amount owed.

persons.name: Jeffrey E. Epstein

keyFacts: The invoice number is 7-133-26200, dated February 13, 2002.
The total amount due on the invoice is $161.94.
The invoice includes charges for duties, taxes, and customs fees related to shipping.
Shipping occurred on February 7, 2002, with delivery on February 13, 2002.
The invoice indicates that charges include amounts paid to French Customs on behalf of Epstein.
